GEORGE WASHINGTON   12 CHERRY STREET    4318392                      
THOMAS JEFFERSON    10 PARK AVENUE      8009999                       
WILLIAM J CLINTON   10 APPLE TREE DRIVE 9994444                       
/*                                                                    
